item.title: CVE-2023-37284|2024-08-02T17:09:34.039Z -- tp-link -- archer%20c20
item.description: Improper authentication vulnerability in Archer C20 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C20(JP)_V1_230616' allows a network-adjacent unauthenticated attacker to execute an arbitrary OS command via a crafted request to bypass authentication.
